name: IQuest-Coder-V1
description: A 40B parameter open-source code LLM released by Ubiquant Investment's IQuest Research Institute. Features Code-Flow multi-stage training that learns from repository evolution and commit history. Claims to match or exceed Claude Sonnet 4.5 and GPT-5.1 on SWE-Bench Verified benchmarks. Fully open-source and self-hostable.
community_quotes: China's first coding AI of 2026 is crushing everything we know
Beating Claude and GPT-5.1 on benchmarks
Fully open source and can be self-hosted
Another DeepSeek moment for Chinese AI
